{"tid":1202236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熟讀五四運動歷史 - 火燒趙家樓事件","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T08:32:04.000Z","uid":218367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7d6e44dbe103d821d6bdbb3bac9eaf56dabbb9","tid":1202236,"uid":218367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"大規模遊行隊伍到達曹宅，數百名軍警早把胡同口封住了，隊伍不得入內。學生向軍警講明來意說：「我們是愛國學生，來這裏是找曹總長談談國事，交換意見，要他愛中國。我們學生手無寸鐵，你們也是中國人，難道你們不愛中國嗎？」軍警於是放行。學生進入胡同，發生暴亂痛打了在曹家串門的章宗祥，並火燒曹宅，引發「火燒趙家樓」事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%BA%94%E5%9B%9B%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8#cite_ref-19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25BF%2590%25E5%258A%25A8%23cite_ref-19&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo4Mqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=32a3f1e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%BA%94%E5%9B%9B%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8#cite_ref-19</a><br />\n<br />\n大家識搵邊個未"}]}